  "detailed_description": "The dark lord has returned, unleashing his horde of monsters on humanity. You must wield the legendary sword and defeat evil, once and for all.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760640/extras/645dc6c3ec14f026861c61d5c3c90e15.poster.avif?t=1765724356\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760640/extras/645dc6c3ec14f026861c61d5c3c90e15.webm?t=1765724356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760640/extras/645dc6c3ec14f026861c61d5c3c90e15.mp4?t=1765724356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Retro 80s graphics with some modern flair<br></li><li>Deliberate gameplay and controls for an oldschool challenge<br></li><li>Catchy chiptune soundtrack and sfx<br></li><li>5 unique sub weapons to pick up on your journey<br></li><li>6 intense stages that will have you fighting to the next checkpoint<br></li><li>Unlock <strong>Expert Mode</strong> for new enemies, areas, and more surprises!<br></li><li><strong>Casual Mode</strong>, for those who prefer unlimited lives and extra checkpoints<br></li><li><strong>Speedrun Modes</strong> for the full game and individual stages</li></ul>",
